have hit me instead.

06:20.467 --> 06:22.947
Impossible.
I'm a dead shot.

06:24.819 --> 06:26.298
What are you doing here?

06:28.126 --> 06:29.998
I was asking you.

06:30.085 --> 06:33.001
Oh, you told me to
keep an eye on Teresa.

06:33.088 --> 06:35.046
Yeah, when I'm not around.

06:35.133 --> 06:37.092
Well, lucky thing
I was here, no?

06:37.135 --> 06:40.008
Hard to say. I'm not used
to that kind of luck.

06:41.139 --> 06:43.403
Ah, French Army.

06:43.490 --> 06:46.144
A real soldier wouldn't
try to kidnap a young girl.

06:46.188 --> 06:48.538
Who are you calling
a young girl?

06:48.669 --> 06:50.279
You all right?

06:50.409 --> 06:53.108
Yes, thanks to Henri.

06:55.197 --> 06:56.851
[Speaking French]

07:00.855 --> 07:03.814
Henri, do me
a favor and go upstairs.

07:03.901 --> 07:06.469
Go upstairs and do what?Just go upstairs.

07:06.600 --> 07:08.906
Right.
[Man coughs]

07:08.993 --> 07:11.779
And take the women
with you.

07:11.822 --> 07:16.044
