38:51.807 --> 38:54.375
Well, I can assure you that
Bozouls is usually quite safe.

38:54.419 --> 38:56.334
These murders are an aberration.

38:56.464 --> 38:58.640
Or a shift in the pattern.

38:58.684 --> 39:01.817
Please, my dear Commandant,
