39:01.904 --> 39:03.906
Oh, no, I couldn't,
I've already eaten too much.

39:04.037 --> 39:07.214
Nonsense, nonsense. I can
see you're a man of appetite,

39:07.301 --> 39:10.435
which according
to an Italian lover I once had

39:10.565 --> 39:13.438
