39:53.869 --> 39:55.349
You keep a gun
under your pillow,

39:55.480 --> 39:57.177
odds are about even
that sooner or later,

39:57.264 --> 39:59.571
you'll take it out
and aim it at someone.

39:59.658 --> 40:01.529
You aim a gun at someone,
the odds are even better

40:01.616 --> 40:03.705
that you'll kill them
or be killed.

40:03.792 --> 40:06.839
And I'm not
that much of a gambler.

40:06.926 --> 40:11.147
A bullet, once fired,
can't be put back in a gun.

40:11.234 --> 40:12.497
I think
with proper training,

40:12.540 --> 40:14.455
